    "course_title": "DANCE HISTORY II: DIRECTIONS AND ISSUES OF CONTEMPORARY DANCE",
    "description": "Surveys dance history from the 1960's to the present. Through research, video viewing, and discussions, grasp aesthetic ideas of modern dance; contextualize the major components of contemporary dance; and characterize trends and styles relative to underlying philosophies.",
